snippet.title: TITANIC VR |  Release Trailer - VR Experience
snippet.description:
Witness the sinking of RMS Titanic. Explore the complete shipwreck. Titanic VR is an immersive educational interactive story and game; with over 6 hours of game-play you will leave with a greater understanding of the historic tragedy that unfolded in 1912.

Visit: www.titanicvr.io
